              corresp="#hamm0054.transcription #hamm0054.translation">
            <p><g type="cross">+</g>ΕΠΙΑΒΔΑΛΛΑΜΑΑΥΙΑΑΜΗΡΑ<lb/> ΑΛΜ<hi rend="ligature"
               >ΟΥ</hi>ΜΕΝΗΝΑΠΕΛΥΘΗΚSΑΝΕ<lb/> ΝΕΩΘΗΟΚΛΙΒΑΝΟϹΤΩΝΕΝΤΑΥ<lb/> ΘΑΔΙΑΑΒΔΑΛΛΑΥΙ<hi rend="ligature"
                  >ΟΥ</hi>ΑΒ<hi rend="ligature">ΟΥ</hi>ΑϹΕΜ<hi rend="ligature">ΟΥ</hi><lb/> ϹΥΜΒ<hi rend="ligature"
                  >ΟΥ</hi>Λ<hi rend="ligature">ΟΥ</hi>ΕΝΜΗΝΗΔΕΚΕΜΒΡΙΩ<lb/> ΠΕΜΠΤΗΗΜΕΡΑΔΕΥΤΕΡΑΙΝΔ<hi rend="superscript"
                  >ϛ</hi>S<lb/> ΕΤΟΥϹΤΗϹΚΟΛΩΝ<hi rend="superscript">ϛ</hi><hi rend="supraline">SΚΨ</hi>ΚΑΤΑΑΡΑΒΑ<lb/>
                  ΕΤ<hi rend="ligature">ΟΥ</hi>Ϲ<hi rend="supraline">ΜΒ</hi>ΕΙϹΙΑϹΗΝΤΩΝΝΟϹ<hi rend="ligature">ΟΥ</hi>Ν<lb/>
                  ΤΩΝϹΠΟΥΔΗΙΩΑΝΝΟΥΜ<hi rend="stacked">Ι</hi>ΓΑΔΑΡΗΝ<hi rend="ligature">ΟΥ</hi>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="edition"
              ana="#b1"
              subtype="transcription"
              xml:id="hamm0054.transcription"
              corresp="#hamm0054.diplomatic #hamm0054.translation">
            <p><g type="cross">+</g> Ἐπὶ Ἀβδάλλα Μαάυια ἀμήρα<lb/> ἀλμουμενὴν ἀπελ<supplied
                  reason="omitted">ο</supplied>ύθη <expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan> ἀνε<lb break="no"/>νεώθη ὁ κλίβανος τῶν ἐνταῦ<lb break="no"/>θα διὰ
               Ἀβδάλλα υἱοῦ Ἀβουασέμου<lb/> συμβούλου, ἐν μηνὴ Δεκεμβρίῳ<lb/> πέμπτῃ, ἡμέρᾳ δευτέρᾳ,
                     <expan><abbr>ἰνδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></expan>
               <num value="6">ς´</num>,<lb/> ἔτους τῆς <expan><abbr>κολων</abbr><ex>ίας</ex></expan>
               <num value="726">ςκψ</num>, κατὰ <expan><abbr>Ἀράβα</abbr><ex>ς</ex></expan>
               <lb/> ἔτους <num value="42">μβ´</num>, εἰς ἴασην τῶν νοσούν<lb break="no"/>των, σπουδῇ Ἰωάννου
                     <expan><abbr>μ</abbr><ex>ειζοτέρου</ex></expan> Γαδαρηνοῦ.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="hamm0054.translation"
              corresp="#hamm0054.diplomatic #hamm0054.transcription">
            <p>In the days of <persName xml:lang="x-Arabic " ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p01">Abdallah Mu'awiya</persName>, the <rs type="religTitle">commander of the faithful</rs>, the clibanus of the <add>baths</add> here was cleared and renewed by <name>
                  <persName xml:lang="x-Arabic " ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p02">Abdallah </persName>
                  <rs type="family">son </rs> of <persName xml:lang="x-Arabic " ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p03">Abu Hashim </persName>
                    </name>, the <rs type="admTitle">governor</rs>, in the <date>month of December, on the fifth day, Monday, in the 6th year of the indiction, in the year 726 of the colony, according to the Arabs the 42nd year</date>, for the healing of the sick, under the care of <persName ref="persons.xml#hamm0054p04">John </persName> the <rs type="ethnicon">Gadarene</rs>, the <rs type="occupation">steward</rs>.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
